---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Software Development';
const description = 'Custom software solutions and technical leadership for B2B SaaS and Financial Services. Full-stack development, architecture, and modernization.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="py-12 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Software Development</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I build custom software solutions that drive business value for B2B SaaS companies and Financial Services firms. Whether you need to develop a new product, modernize legacy systems, or scale your engineering capabilities, I provide hands-on technical leadership and development expertise.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Services</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">B2B SaaS Applications</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Multi-tenant platforms</li>
              <li>• API-first architecture</li>
              <li>• Subscription billing</li>
              <li>• Customer portals</li>
              <li>• Integration marketplace</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Financial Services</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Trading platforms</li>
              <li>• Portfolio management</li>
              <li>• Risk analysis tools</li>
              <li>• Payment processing</li>
              <li>• Regulatory reporting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Enterprise Applications</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Workflow automation</li>
              <li>• CRM systems</li>
              <li>• ERP customization</li>
              <li>• Business intelligence</li>
              <li>• Document management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Technical Architecture & Leadership</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">System Design</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Software architecture & tech stack selection</li>
              <li>Scalability planning</li>
              <li>Cloud-native architecture (AWS, Azure, GCP)</li>
              <li>Microservices patterns</li>
              <li>API design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Engineering Leadership</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Team structure and hiring</li>
              <li>Development processes</li>
              <li>Code review & quality standards</li>
              <li>Technical debt management</li>
              <li>Performance optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Technology Stack Expertise</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Backend</h4>
            <p>Python, Java, Node.js, Go, Django, Spring Boot, FastAPI</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h4>
            <p>Angular, React, Vue.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Databases</h4>
            <p>PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Cloud & DevOps</h4>
            <p>AWS, Azure, GCP, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Modernization & Migration</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Assessment of technical debt and modernization opportunities</li>
          <li>Strangler pattern migration strategies</li>
          <li>Re-platforming to cloud infrastructure</li>
          <li>Database optimization and scaling</li>
          <li>Zero-downtime migration planning</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Common Challenges I Solve</h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">B2B SaaS Scale-ups:</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>• "Our platform can't handle customer growth"</li>
            <li>• "We need to ship features faster without breaking things"</li>
            <li>• "Our technical debt is slowing us down"</li>
            <li>• "We need better security and compliance"</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Financial Services:</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• "We need to modernize our trading platform"</li>
            <li>• "Regulatory requirements are slowing development"</li>
            <li>• "We can't integrate with modern fintech APIs"</li>
            <li>• "Our systems don't scale for market volatility"</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Engagement Models</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Project-Based Development</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-2">Fixed scope and timeline for MVPs, features, or migrations (3-6 months)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Staff Augmentation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-2">Embedded senior developer or architect (2-5 days/week)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Technical Leadership Retainer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-2">Fractional CTO/VP Engineering (1-2 days/week)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Discovery & Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-2">Technical assessment and design (2-4 weeks, fixed fee)</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Quality Guarantees</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Code Quality:</strong> Industry-standard practices, automated testing, code review</li>
          <li><strong>Security:</strong> OWASP compliance, security scanning, penetration testing</li>
          <li><strong>Performance:</strong> SLA-driven response times, load testing</li>
          <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Technical specs, API docs, deployment guides</li>
          <li><strong>Support:</strong> Post-launch support, bug fixes, maintenance options</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Need to build or scale your software platform?</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Let's discuss how I can help you solve complex technical challenges and deliver high-quality software solutions.</p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/beaumois/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
